data.text: And to those who can get vaccinated but haven't get - please do so ASAP! You will literally be saving lives! #GetVaccinatedASAP

That said, there is still much work to do in getting equitable vaccine access to those who are being left behind - both in the U.S. and abroad. We each have an obligation to help get shots into the arms of anyone and everyone who wants them. #VaccineEquity
